      "source": [
        "# 📘 Deep Learning Text Generation Learning Project\n",
        "## Text Generation using **Vanilla RNN, LSTM, and GRU**\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook is built for **students and beginners** to understand how sequence models learn:\n",
        "- grammar\n",
        "- sentence flow\n",
        "- contextual dependencies\n",
        "- next-word prediction\n",
        "- text generation\n",
        "\n",
        "🎯 **Goal:** Compare **Simple RNN vs LSTM vs GRU** on the same text corpus and understand why gated architectures perform better."
      ],
      "id": "DF-ul5G_MLu_"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1bKmjlPrbV89"
      },
